rows.label: qst201219_0010
rows.name: That's a nice smile.

rows.label: qst201219_0020
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Huh?

rows.label: qst201219_0030
rows.name:
See? You can do it. ...So
you can smile, Seori.

rows.label: qst201219_0040
rows.name: I... was smiling?

rows.label: qst201219_0050
rows.name:
After all that hard work from both of
you, of course you'd smile naturally.

rows.label: qst201219_0060
rows.name:
Here, Seori. Why don't
you go join Mikumari?

rows.label: qst201219_0070
rows.name: ...No, it's fine.

rows.label: qst201219_0080
rows.name:
Why not? You worked hard too,
Seori. Go have some fun together.

rows.label: qst201219_0090
rows.name:
...I didn't do anything. This is
all thanks to Mikumari's efforts.

rows.label: qst201219_0100
rows.name:
It was Mikumari's refusal to give up
that made everyone in town smile.

rows.label: qst201219_0110
rows.name: No, it's thanks to both of you.

rows.label: qst201219_0120
rows.name: That's right.

rows.label: qst201219_0130
rows.name:
I think Mikumari didn't give up precisely
because you were there, Seori.

rows.label: qst201219_0140
rows.name:
And it was because you two sisters worked
so hard that everyone in town is smiling.

rows.label: qst201219_0150
rows.name:
Brothers and sisters are beings who
acknowledge and complement each other.

rows.label: qst201219_0160
rows.name: The two of us...

rows.label: qst201219_0170
rows.name: Seori! Over here!

rows.label: qst201219_0180
rows.name: They want to play with us!

rows.label: qst201219_0190
rows.name: Go on.

rows.label: qst201219_0200
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: qst201219_0210
rows.name: ...Okay.

rows.label: qst201219_0220
rows.name: ...Honestly, what a handful.

rows.label: qst201219_0230
rows.name:
My big sister gets lonely if
I'm not around, after all.

rows.label: qst201219_0240
rows.name:
What's that supposed to mean? I
can manage just fine on my own!

rows.label: qst201219_0250
rows.name:
Wait, did you just...
call me "big sister"?

rows.label: qst201219_0260
rows.name: ...I did not.

rows.label: qst201219_0270
rows.name: You're lying! You totally did!

rows.label: qst201219_0280
rows.name: I did not.

rows.label: qst201219_0290
rows.name:
Hey, let's hurry up! They're
going to start without us!

rows.label: qst201219_0300
rows.name: Yeah, yeah! Quick, quick!

rows.label: qst201219_0310
rows.name: C'mon, say it one more time!

rows.label: qst201219_0320
rows.name: I don't know what you're talking about.
